data.description: Huge price reduction!!! This extraordinary home with an incredible finished basement in the popular area of Mainstreet in Stone Mountain! New custom kitchen with solid surface countertops. Spacious open family room & dining area. Family room with fireplace. Newly Updated bathrooms. Large master suite with walk-in closet & large master bathroom. Large deck overlooking the backyard with landscaped lawn. Create unforgettable moments with family and friends, whether you're hosting a lively barbecue, a tranquil evening under the stars, or a fun-filled gathering. Convenient to neighboring counties of Gwinnett and Rockdale. Too much to mention!
